data.description: Rare Nw Cape Coral Pool Home on TRIPLE lot. You have space between you and your neighbors. Imagine sitting on your  oversized back lanai sipping your morning coffee watching the beautiful SWFL sunrise. You can watch the beautiful sunset from the front sitting room  You don't want to miss this beautiful home. Inside you will find 4 bedroom 2 bath 1993 sq ft home. You have a 2 car attached garage. And not to mention just a little over 1000 sq ft anai area with lots of shade and a salt water pool.  Beautiful quartz countertops, You have a walk in closet in the  owners  bedroom that overlooks the  pool and Lanai area that has been screened in.  You can fall asleep with the waterfall feature going on in the pool area. If you love being outside then this home is for you. The yard is fenced in for plenty of room for kids or pets. New roof 2020. Don't miss out on this move in ready home.
